'''Steven Blount''' is an actor in ''[[Game of Thrones]]''. He plays the part of [[Rickard Karstark]]. Originally [[Vinnie McCabe]] has been announced in the role of Rickard Karstark, however he turned out to be playing a [[House Lannister|Lannister]] bannerman, [[Leo Lefford]], in the same episode. Blount's CV lists him as playing Lord Karstark.&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.firstcallmanagement.ie/STEVE%20BLOUNT.html Steven Blount's CV at First Call Management.]&lt;/ref&gt;

For the [[Season 2|second season]] it was announced that [[John Stahl]] was playing Rickard Karstark.&lt;ref&gt;[http://grrm.livejournal.com/243470.html George R.R. Martin's blog]&lt;/ref&gt; Since Blount's character was never named as Karstark on-screen, it is unclear if he will continue (with the character retrospectively changed to another, miscellaneous Northern lord) or if Stahl is actually replacing him.

